TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT CUSTOMERS.CUSTOMER_NUM, CUSTOMERS.FIRSTNAME, CUSTOMERS.LASTNAME, CUSTOMERS.EMAIL, CUSTOMERS.PHONE, CUSTOMERS.ADDRESS, CUSTOMERS.CITY, CUSTOMERS.STATE, CUSTOMERS.ZIPCODE, CUSTOMERS.LASTMODIFIED FROM CUSTOMERS WHERE lastmodified > TO_DATE( '$$V_LAST_RUN', 'MM/DD/YYYY HH24:MI:SS')

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT DIMCUSTOMERS.SURROGATEKEY as SURROGATEKEY, DIMCUSTOMERS.FIRSTNAME as FIRSTNAME, DIMCUSTOMERS.LASTNAME as LASTNAME, DIMCUSTOMERS.EMAIL as EMAIL, DIMCUSTOMERS.PHONE as PHONE, DIMCUSTOMERS.ADDRESS as ADDRESS, DIMCUSTOMERS.CITY as CITY, DIMCUSTOMERS.STATE as STATE, DIMCUSTOMERS.ZIPCODE as ZIPCODE, DIMCUSTOMERS.LASTMODIFIED as LASTMODIFIED, DIMCUSTOMERS.STARTDATE as STARTDATE, DIMCUSTOMERS.ENDDATE as ENDDATE, DIMCUSTOMERS.CHGE_CURRENT_IND as CHGE_CURRENT_IND, DIMCUSTOMERS.CUSTOMERID as CUSTOMERID FROM DIMCUSTOMERS WHERE CHGE_CURRENT_IND = 'Y'

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF( NOT ISNULL(LKP_CUSTOMERID) AND LKP_PHONE != PHONE , 'TRUE', 'FALSE')
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: UPDATE_REC

GROUP.DESCRIPTION: Path for the data when none of the group conditions are satisfied.
GROUP.NAME: DEFAULT1
